{
  "texts": [
    "We gathered seven datasets, each possessing unique traits that distinguish them from one another.",
    "The Heterogeneity Human Activity Recognition (HHAR) dataset [37] showcases a diverse range of smartphone and smartwatch models, adding to our variability.",
    "MobiAct [38] includes 61 subjects, making it the dataset with the largest subject count in our collection.",
    "MotionSense [39] exclusively comprises data collected from Apple iPhones, setting it apart from the rest.",
    "RealWorld [40] brings in further diversity by incorporating seven on-body positions."
  ]
}